what "staying out of it" means.

383
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:29,190
I'm only here to help
Prince Wuxia clear his name.

384
00:23:33,870 --> 00:23:34,800
In that case,

385
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,520
why don't we split up the work?

386
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:37,960
That way, we can save some time.

387
00:23:42,430 --> 00:23:44,760
Do you know
why I brought you in for questioning?

388
00:23:45,150 --> 00:23:45,830
No.

389
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:51,320
Was Prince Wuhen a regular here?

390
