only you served him?

395
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:06,390
I suppose he found me pleasing.

396
00:24:07,150 --> 00:24:08,910
A beauty like you

397
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:11,150
is hard for any man to resist.

398
00:24:12,430 --> 00:24:13,320
But

399
00:24:13,730 --> 00:24:14,920
