402
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:20,720
Recently,
these two dishes kept showing up.

403
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:23,190
Braised soft-shelled turtle and lamb
with pickled amaranth.

404
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:25,320
Soft-shelled turtle and amaranth
don't go together,

405
00:24:25,480 --> 00:24:27,000
