the guest away.

414
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:44,910
And it just so happened,

415
00:24:45,670 --> 00:24:47,480
after Prince Wuxia left that night,

416
00:24:48,150 --> 00:24:49,800
someone else ordered
the same two dishes.

417
00:24:51,150 --> 00:24:52,280
As expected,

418
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:54,240
you took this person away.

419
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:56,110
Aiding in leaking the exam

420
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:58,190
could get your entire clan executed.

421
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:01,590
If you tell me
who Prince Wuhen met that night,

422
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:03,670
I'll spare your life.

423
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:05,430
If I were you,

424
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:06,960
I would tell everything I know

425
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:09,910
to save my family

426
00:25:10,590 --> 00:25:13,080
since the matter has been exposed.

427
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:16,670
I'll talk.

428
00:25:17,670 --> 00:25:18,720
- Meng Huairui?
- Meng Huairui?

429
00:25:19,870 --> 00:25:21,960
Zhan Lu, take Meng Huairui in now!

430
00:25:22,670 --> 00:25:23,240
Yes, sir.

431
00:25:31,830 --> 00:25:32,520
Zhenzhen?

432
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,190
You came alone?

433
00:25:34,870 --> 00:25:36,280
Why didn't you bring your maid?

434
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:38,870
Are you going somewhere?

435
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:42,280
My uncle is gravely ill.

436
00:25:42,280 --> 00:25:44,080
