438
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,080
Zhenzhen,

439
00:25:50,170 --> 00:25:51,350
I'm in a rush.

440
00:25:51,430 --> 00:25:52,830
If you'll excuse me, I have...

441
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:53,430
