442
00:25:57,430 --> 00:25:58,430
Huairui...

443
00:25:58,670 --> 00:25:59,320
Father.

444
00:26:00,040 --> 00:26:00,720
Mother.

445
00:26:06,190 --> 00:26:07,190
I didn't kill him.

446
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,480
I only gave him a little push.

447
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:11,590
Prince Wuhen hit his head and died.

448
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:14,390
That day,

449
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:17,150
I went to Chunyue Pavilion
to buy the exam questions.

450
00:26:17,630 --> 00:26:18,520
But before I arrived,

451
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:20,320
Prince Wuxia and Prince Wuhen

452
00:26:20,320 --> 00:26:21,150
