453
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:24,150
Prince Wuhen took it out on me.

454
00:26:24,670 --> 00:26:25,280
Your Highness,

455
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,590
someone is here to see you.

456
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,630
Meng Huairui, at your service.

457
00:26:39,760 --> 00:26:40,760
The Meng family, huh?

458
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:44,480
Do you think
anyone can just walk in here?

459
00:26:48,760 --> 00:26:49,520
Prince Wuhen,

460
00:26:52,390 --> 00:26:53,630
don't be so quick

461
00:26:54,390 --> 00:26:55,760
