this is all just a coincidence!

466
00:27:11,130 --> 00:27:13,250
It truly has nothing to do with me.

467
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:15,870
I only came to purchase a jade pendant.

468
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:22,670
The Mengs are always full of schemes.

469
00:27:23,150 --> 00:27:23,760
