476
00:27:53,910 --> 00:27:54,520
Prince Wuhen...

477
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:55,560
Prince Wuhen...

478
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:29,590
Zhenzhen.

479
00:28:30,870 --> 00:28:31,630
Ms. Zhenzhen,

480
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:34,000
