a terrible end.

494
00:29:02,150 --> 00:29:04,000
Shen Zaiye is investigating
this himself.

495
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:06,190
If it leads back to you,

496
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,670
have you thought
about what to answer him?

497
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:12,280
I...

498
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,190
I'll tell the truth

499
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:16,830
and leave it to fate.

500
00:29:20,630 --> 00:29:23,190
Ms. Zhenzhen, blame me if you must.

501
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:24,870
But please spare my parents.

502
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:25,870
Ms. Zhenzhen.

503
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,110
I ask you one more time.

504
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,760
If it leads back to you,

505
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:33,000
what will you answer?

506
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:35,960
I...

507
00:29:39,590 --> 00:29:40,630
Ms. Zhenzhen,

508
00:29:41,040 --> 00:29:43,080
I will answer
however you want me to answer.

509
00:29:43,560 --> 00:29:44,720
Let my parents go.

510
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:45,720
Please...

511
00:29:47,080 --> 00:29:48,000
Ms. Zhenzhen.

512
00:29:48,190 --> 00:29:48,720
Ms. Zhenzhen.

513
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:51,800
As long as we catch Meng Huairui,

514
00:29:52,150 --> 00:29:53,190
we can save Prince Wuxia.

515
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:54,910
That's right.

516
00:29:56,150 --> 00:29:57,240
There are still two details

517
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:58,720
that are suspicious.

518
00:29:59,520 --> 00:30:00,350
What details?

519
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:01,960
First,

520
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:04,720
