of the table don't line up.

521
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:08,670
We need to confirm

522
00:30:09,120 --> 00:30:10,760
whether the shape
of Prince Wuhen's wound

523
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:12,560
matches the ones on the table.

524
00:30:15,210 --> 00:30:16,150
And the second?

525
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:17,440
Have you seen

526
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:18,760
