00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:36,480
he wouldn't have died such
a miserable death.

555
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,190
Your Highness,

556
00:31:37,560 --> 00:31:39,080
our spies at the jade workshop report

557
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:41,390
that Miss Meng has collapsed
from poison.

558
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:48,240
She's just a pawn gone bad.

559
00:31:48,830 --> 00:31:49,480
It's nothing.

560
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:50,870
Please continue.

561
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:52,800
Your Highness,

562
00:31:53,320 --> 00:31:55,800
Shen Zaiye is still combing the city
for jade craftsmen.

563
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:58,190
I'm worried
he'll trace the craftsman back

564
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,800
to our Meng family.

565
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:00,590
Oh, right.

566
00:32:01,390 --> 00:32:03,350
The craftsman came from your family.

567
00:32:03,830 --> 00:32:06,110
So is Meng Huairui.

568
00:32:06,630 --> 00:32:07,520
I guess

569
00:32:07,830 --> 00:32:10,110
Meng Huairui joined hands with Wuhen

570
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:12,390
for fame and fortune.

571
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:15,430
In the end, things went sideways,
and they argued.

572
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:16,760
Then someone died.

573
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,480
And what does that have to do with us?

574
00:32:20,190 --> 00:32:21,800
The real question is,

575
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:23,720
will you be willing
to sacrifice a clansman?

576
00:32:24,320 --> 00:32:26,080
That Meng Huairui deserves
what's coming.

577
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:28,000
What worries me now

578
00:32:28,590 --> 00:32:30,430
is Shen Zaiye using this matter

579
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:31,960
to trace it further

580
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:33,670
and expose more secrets.

581
00:32:34,670 --> 00:32:35,720
If he does,

582
00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:37,960
we weigh the cost.

583
00:32:38,870 --> 00:32:40,590
He's placing his next move on my piece.

584
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:41,870
Why should you fear?

585
00:32:52,420 --> 00:32:53,630
(Yiyun Residence)

586
00:32:53,630 --> 00:32:54,190
Someone!

587
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,590
Imperial Physician Bai, save her!

588
00:32:56,110 --> 00:32:57,000
Chancellor, this way.

589
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:59,280
Imperial Physician Bai,
how's the antidote coming along?

590
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,960
Chancellor, it's still in development.

591
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,870
For now,

592
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:05,320
I can only prescribe
a pain-relieving powder

593
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,590
to ease her symptoms.

594
00:33:06,590 --> 00:33:07,430
All right.

595
00:33:07,670 --> 00:33:08,390
Follow me.

596
00:33:18,140 --> 00:33:18,670
Chancellor,

597
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:20,350
Meng Huairui's residence was ransacked,

598
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,560
and he's nowhere to be found.

599
00:33:21,560 --> 00:33:23,080
Also, Meng Zhenzhen wants to see you.

600
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:24,760
She said you'll regret it if you refuse.

601
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:28,080
If anything happens to Taohua,
report to me immediately.

602
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:28,560
Yes. sir.

603
00:33:30,870 --> 00:33:31,670
Get to the point.

604
00:33:31,910 --> 00:33:33,480
Why are you here?

605
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,800
It's been a while.

606
00:33:40,910 --> 00:33:41,720
I'm here

607
00:33:42,150 --> 00:33:43,480
to make you a deal.

608
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:45,160
For Meng Huairui?

609
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:48,150
Catching him is only a matter of time.

610
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:50,760
The Meng family is willing
to hand him over

611
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:52,480
and do whatever you want with him.

612
00:33:52,870 --> 00:33:54,480
But this matter ends there.

613
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,390
You must not drag
the Meng family into it.

614
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:57,600
Why would I agree to that?

615
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,190
Because of Jiang Taohua's life.

616
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:03,590
I hear she's been poisoned.

617
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:07,040
She must be in terrible pain by now.

618
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:10,310
So the Meng family has sided

619
00:34:10,750 --> 00:34:12,110
with Prince Wuyin.

620
00:34:13,710 --> 00:34:14,790
No need for small talk.

621
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:17,440
Do you want

622
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,310
the antidote or not?

623
00:34:21,750 --> 00:34:23,040
Whether it's destroyed or not

624
00:34:23,710 --> 00:34:25,360
depends entirely on you.

625
00:34:29,270 --> 00:34:30,270
How do I know

626
00:34:30,590 --> 00:34:32,040
this antidote is even real?

627
00:34:32,560 --> 00:34:33,880
How do you want me to prove it?

628
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:34,670
Test it.

629
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,960
If anything happens to Jiang Taohua,

630
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:38,400
I'll hold you responsible.

631
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:51,040
The antidote works.

632
00:35:51,660 --> 00:35:53,310
Then I'll hand over Meng Huairui to you.

633
00:35:54,270 --> 00:35:56,310
What I want isn't just a temporary fix

634
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:57,790
but the permanent cure.

635
00:35:58,790 --> 00:36:00,080
Give me the permanent cure.

636
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,630
Then I'll let your family go.

637
00:36:02,200 --> 00:36:03,190
You should've said that

638
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,840
before we tested the medicine.

639
00:36:05,110 --> 00:36:05,710
You're the one

640
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:07,790
who came to make a deal.

641
00:36:08,790 --> 00:36:10,590
I never agreed to anything.

642
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:13,480
Let me be honest.

643
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,190
I don't have the permanent cure.

644
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:17,270
All I have are these two pills.

645
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,880
If you want them,

646
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:20,750
I'll give them both.

647
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:22,560
If not,

648
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,790
next time the poison flares up,

649
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:27,000
she might not be so lucky.

650
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:36,710
Leave the antidote.

651
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,630
I want Meng Huairui taken alive
to the imperial prison.

652
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:41,040
This time,

653
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:43,080
I'll let the Meng family go.

654
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,880
You have my word, Chancellor Shen.

655
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,040
I'll take care of it.

656
00:37:04,150 --> 00:37:04,710
Zhan Lu.

657
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:05,320
Yes, sir.

658
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:07,000
Give the pills
to Imperial Physician Bai.

659
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:09,160
Have him work on developing
the full cure immediately.

660
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:09,560
Yes, sir.

661
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,840
(He actually gave in for me.)

662
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:15,270
(Just like that,
he let the Meng family off the hook.)

663
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:21,960
Imperial Physician Bai

664
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,960
will work on the permanent cure.

665
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:25,880
You can rest here without worry.

666
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:28,190
Chancellor.

667
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,270
These will last for two months.

668
00:37:41,680 --> 00:37:43,590
Thank you for the medicine,
Chancellor Shen.

669
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,750
I must return
to Prince Wuyin's residence now.

670
00:37:53,750 --> 00:37:54,310
Very well.

671
00:38:16,790 --> 00:38:18,080
(That lotus-shaped mark...)

672
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:21,710
(Why do Jiang Taohua's
shoe prints match)

673
00:38:21,710 --> 00:38:23,150
(with the ones at the crime scene?)

674
00:38:24,110 --> 00:38:24,880
(Or could it be)

675
00:38:25,310 --> 00:38:27,310
(that everyone
at Prince Wuyin's residence)

676
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:28,880
(wears the same kind of shoes?)

677
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:51,450
♪The flower bloomed,
knowing nothing at all♪

678
00:38:51,450 --> 00:38:54,480
♪In splendor, proud and tall♪

679
00:38:55,390 --> 00:38:58,620
♪The flower fell, lashed by the wind♪

680
00:38:58,620 --> 00:39:02,380
♪In a daze,
it felt like lifetimes had thinned♪

681
00:39:02,680 --> 00:39:05,860
♪Petals soaked in rain♪

682
00:39:05,860 --> 00:39:09,200
♪Heartbreak follows again and again♪

683
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:13,250
♪The flower weeps, burdened by thoughts♪

684
00:39:13,250 --> 00:39:18,970
♪With no one it can be brought♪

685
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:30,850
♪Wishes struggle through the mire♪

686
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:38,100
♪Regrets clash in hopeless fire♪

687
00:39:38,610 --> 00:39:45,610
♪Still I hope she'll pick the flower
kissed by dew♪

688
00:39:45,910 --> 00:39:50,060
♪Even if it means this flower♪

689
00:39:50,060 --> 00:39:57,030
♪Will be hers to give to someone new♪

690
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:11,360
♪Whose eyes
did the flower's heart meet?♪

691
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:14,610
♪Love and hate held back, discreet♪

692
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:18,740
♪The flower withers, feelings in decay♪

693
00:40:18,740 --> 00:40:25,320
♪No longer needing to say♪

694
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:36,320
♪Yet I still long for her in madness♪

695
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:43,680
♪Unafraid of judgment or sadness♪

696
00:40:44,020 --> 00:40:51,020
♪Remembering the words
she spoke of flowers and skies♪

697
00:40:51,390 --> 00:40:53,160
♪And finding♪

698
00:40:53,160 --> 00:41:02,160
♪They were her gentle heart's reply♪

